The key to Cortana's success will be knowing where a user
is, what time it is, and what they are trying to do. Albert
Einstein's work on the relationship between space and time gave
rise to Microsoft's secret project name, said Horvitz.

'Einstein was brilliant about space and time,' he said.
'It's using brilliance about space and time generally in our
agents.'


